'''顯微鏡座AU'''（AU Mic）是距離我們{{Convert|32.3|ly|pc|abbr=off|lk=on}}遠，大約是離[[太陽|太陽]]最近距離恆星8倍遠的一顆[[紅矮星|紅矮星]]<ref name="KALASETAL04"/>。它的[[視星等|視星等]]為8.73 <ref name=aaa460_3_695/>，這是太黯淡了，因此裸眼看不見它。因為它是在南天[[顯微鏡座|顯微鏡座]]的一顆[[變星|變星]]，所以用[[變星命名法|變星命名法]]命名。如同[[老人增四|老人增四]]（繪架座β）一樣，它有一個[[岩屑盤|岩屑盤]]的塵埃拱星盤環繞著。

== 恆星的性質 ==
顯微鏡座AU是一顆年輕的恆星，只有1,200萬年的歷史；還不到太陽年齡的1%<ref name="PLAVCHANETAL05"/>，[[恆星光譜|恆星光譜]]類型為M1Ve<ref name=aaa460_3_695/>，是一顆[[紅矮星|紅矮星]]<ref name=baas23_1382/>。它的半徑為[[太陽|太陽]]的60%，儘管質量超過太陽的一半<ref name="DELZANNA2002"/><ref name=sci303_5666_1982/>，它的輻射量只有太陽的9%<ref name=apj698_2_1068/>，比太陽少了許多。這些能量從[[恆星大氣層|表面]]釋出，溫度只有3,700[[熱力學溫標|K]]<ref name = "LINSKYETAL82"/>，使它發出涼爽的橙紅色光<ref name=csiro/>。顯微鏡座AU是[[繪架座β移動星群|繪架座β移動星群]]的成員之一<ref name=araa41_1_685/><ref name=apj520_2_L123/>，它可能受到[[顯微鏡座AT|顯微鏡座AT]]的[[引力結合能|重力約束]]，兩者構成[[聯星|聯星]] <ref name=aaa302_193/>。

從[[無線電|無線電]]到[[X射線|X射線]]，在所有的[[電磁頻譜|電磁頻譜]]上都觀察得到顯微鏡座AU，並且在所有的這些波段都觀測到[[耀星|閃焰]]的活動<ref name=apj421_2_800/><ref name=apj414_2_L49/><ref name=apj312_822/><ref name = "TSIKOUDI2000"/>。這些閃焰在1973年首度被發現<ref name=apjs25_1/><ref name=mnras197_815/>，在這些隨機的爆發之後，其亮度幾乎是[[正弦|正弦]]式變化，週期為4.865天，而振幅隨時間的變化很緩慢。在1971年測量[[UBV測光系統|V波段]]的變化只有0.3[[絕對星等|星等]]；到1980年，更只有0.1星等<ref name=aaa174_1_139/>。

== 岩屑盤 ==
[[File:Debris_disk_AU_Mic_HST.jpg|left]]的顯微鏡座AU[[岩屑盤|岩屑盤]]影像。]]
[[File:Mysterious_ripples_moving_through_the_disc_of_AU_Microscopii.webm|thumb]]

在2003年，[[保羅·卡拉斯|保羅·卡拉斯]]和他的研究夥伴首度使用[[夏威夷|夏威夷]][[毛納基山天文台|毛納基山天文台]]2.2米口徑的望遠鏡，在可見光的波段解析出顯微鏡座AU有塵埃的[[星周盤|星周盤]]<ref name = "KALASETAL04" />這些大的岩屑盤以側面朝向著地球疔瀟。苽擭<ref>{{cite journal|author = Paul Kalas, James R. Graham and Mark Clampin|title = A planetary system as the origin of structure in Fomalhaut's dust belt|journal = Nature|volume = 435|date = 2005-06-23|pages = 1067–1070|url = http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2005Natur.435.1067K|doi = 10.1038/nature03601|issue = 7045|access-date = 2008-10-24|archive-date = 2012-06-09|archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/68HxydQ0D?url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2005Natur.435.1067K|dead-url = no}}</ref>，測量到其半徑至少有200[[天文單位|天文單位]]距離恆星有如此大的距離疔瀟。苽擭，盤中塵埃的[[壽命|壽命]]足以超過顯微鏡 AU現在的年齡<ref name = "KALASETAL04" />盤中氣體和塵埃粒子的質量比率大約是疔瀟。苽擭6：1，遠低於通常假設的100：1的初始值<ref name="ROBERGEETAL05">{{cite journal|author = Aki Roberge, Alycia J. Weinberger, Seth Redfield, and Paul D. Feldman|title = Rapid Dissipation of Primordial Gas from the AU Microscopii Debris Disk|journal = The Astrophysical Journal|date = 2005-06-20|volume = 626|issue = 2|pages = L105–L108|url = http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2005ApJ...626L.105R|doi = 10.1086/431899|access-date = 2008-10-24|archive-date = 2012-06-09|archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/68Hxz3p92?url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2005ApJ...626L.105R|dead-url = no}}</ref>，因此被歸類為"缺乏氣體"的岩屑盤估計在可見的盤中氣體總量大約相當於月球的質量疔瀟。苽擭，而當塵埃產生成更大的[[星子|星子]]時，估計質量至少是月球的6倍<ref>{{cite journal|author = C. H. Chen, B. M. Patten, M. W. Werner, C. D. Dowell, K. R. Stapelfeldt, I. Song, J. R. Stauffer, M. Blaylock, K. D. Gordon, and V. Krause|title = A Spitzer Study of Dusty Disks around Nearby, Young Stars|journal = The Astrophysical Journal|date = 2005-12-01|volume = 634|issue = 2|pages = 1372–1384|url = http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2005ApJ...634.1372C|doi = 10.1086/497124|access-date = 2008-10-24|archive-date = 2012-06-09|archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/68HxzUlpE?url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2005ApJ...634.1372C|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

顯微鏡座AU的[[天文光譜學|光譜能量分佈]]在[[次微米天文學|次微米]]波長上顯示岩屑盤內有一個擴展到17天文單位的洞孔<ref>{{cite journal|title = A Submillimeter Search of Nearby Young Stars for Cold Dust: Discovery of Debris Disks around Two Low-Mass Stars|author = Michael C. Liu, Brenda C. Matthews, Jonathan P. Williams, and Paul G. Kalas|journal = [[The_Astrophysical_Journal|The Astrophysical Journal]]|date = 2004-06-10|volume = 608|issue = 1|pages = 526–532|url = http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2004ApJ...608..526L|doi = 10.1086/392531|access-date = 2008-10-24|archive-date = 2012-04-03|archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/66e70DgoA?url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2004ApJ...608..526L|dead-url = no}}</ref>，而散射光的影像估計洞孔的半徑是12天文單位<ref name = "KIRSTETAL05">{{cite journal|author = John E. Kirst, D. R. Ardila, D. A. Golimowski, M. Clampin, H. C. Ford, G. D. Illingworth, G. F. Hartig, F. Bartko, N. Benítez, J. P. Blakeslee, R. J. Bouwens, L. D. Bradley, T. J. Broadhurst, R. A. Brown, C. J. Burrows, E. S. Cheng, N. J. G. Cross, R. Demarco, P. D. Feldman, M. Franx, T. Goto, C. Gronwall, B. Holden, N. Homeier, L. Infante, R. A. Kimble, M. P. Lesser, A. R. Martel, S. Mei, F. Mennanteau, G. R. Meurer, G. K. Miley, V. Motta, M. Postman, P. Rosati, M. Sirianni, W. B. Sparks, H. D. Tran, Z. I. Tsvetanov, R. L. White, AND W. Zheng|title = Hubble Space Telescope Advanced Camera for Surveys Coronagraphic Imaging of the AU Microscopii Debris Disk|journal = The Astronomical Journal|volume = 129|issue = 2|pages = 1008–1017|url = http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2005AJ....129.1008K|doi = 10.1086/426755|date=February 2005}}</ref>結合光譜能量分佈和表面的亮度疔瀟。苽擭，估計洞孔的半徑更小，只有1-10天文單位<ref name = "METCHEVETAL05">{{cite journal|author = Stanimir A. Metchev, Joshua A. Eisner, and Lynne A. Hillenbrand|title = Adaptive Optics Imaging of the AU Microscopii Circumstellar Disk: Evidence for Dynamical Evolution|journal = The Astrophysical Journal|date = 2005-03-20 |volume = 622|issue = 1|pages = 451–462|url = http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2005ApJ...622..451M|doi = 10.1086/427869}}</ref>。
在40天文單位之內，盤的內部結構顯示出是[[非對稱|非對稱]]的<ref name = "LIU04">{{cite journal|title = Substructure in the Circumstellar Disk Around the Young Star AU Microscopii|author = Michael C. Liu|journal = Science|date = 2004-09-03|volume = 305|number = 5689|pages = 1442–1444|url = http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/full/305/5689/1442|doi = 10.1126/science.1102929|pmid = 15308766|access-date = 2008-10-24|archive-date = 2012-04-03|archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/66e70gyJE?url=http://www.sciencemag.org/content/305/5689/1442.full|dead-url = no}}</ref>，內部的結構已經與受到較大天體影響或最近有行星形成的比較，期望能看見更大的身影<ref name = "LIU04"/>。

出現在內部的洞孔和不對稱引導了很多的天文學家在此搜尋行星循著顯微鏡疔瀟。苽擭 AU的軌道，迄2007年尚無任何可以導致行星的發現<ref name = "METCHEVETAL05" /><ref name = "MASCIADRIETAL05">{{cite journal|author = E. Masciadri, R. Mundt, Th. Henning, and C. Alvarez|title = A Search for Hot Massive Extrasolar Planets around Nearby Young Stars with the Adaptive Optics System NACO|journal = The Astrophysical Journal|date = 2005-06-01 |volume = 625|issue = 2|pages = 1004–1018|url = http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2005ApJ...625.1004M|doi = 10.1086/429687}}</ref>。

盤面上的表面亮度(單位面積的亮度)是從恆星的投影距離<math>b</math>和形狀特性的函數在盤面內側疔瀟。苽擭15天文單位距離內的密度似乎是一個定值<ref name = "KIRSTETAL05" />，大約<math>b \approx 15 AU</math>密度開始降低；開始減緩的較慢，大約是<math>b^{-\alpha}</math> 此處<math>\alpha \approx 1.8</math>；再往外<math>b \approx 43 AU</math>，光度下降得更陡峭，大約是 <math>b^{-\alpha}</math>，此處<math>\alpha \approx 4.8</math><ref name = "KIRSTETAL05" />這種疔瀟。苽擭"破裂幂律"形狀與[[繪架座β|繪架座β]]的盤面輪廓非常相似。

== 觀測的方法 ==
顯微鏡座AU的盤面已經被各種不同波段的[[波長|波長]]觀測過，給了我們這個系統不同型態的資訊在疔瀟。苽擭[[可見光|光學波長]]下觀測到的光線是恆星的光，它們被塵埃粒子反射(散射)進入我們的視線內觀察這些波長時疔瀟。苽擭，利用[[日冕儀|日冕儀遮版]]阻擋直接來自恆星的光，這樣可以提供高分辨率的盤面影像因為波長比塵埃粒子直徑大的光波不易被散射疔瀟。苽擭，在不同的波長上比較(例如，可見光和紅外線)就可以得知盤面上塵埃粒子尺寸大小的訊息<ref name="ucbn0108">{{cite news | first=Robert | last=Sanders | title=Dust around nearby star like powder snow | publisher=UC Berkeley News | date=2007-01-08 | url=http://www.berkeley.edu/news/media/releases/2007/01/08_dust.shtml | accessdate=2007-01-11 | archive-date=2007-01-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070115065231/http://www.berkeley.edu/news/media/releases/2007/01/08_dust.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

